def select_features_KBest(x,y):
    selector = SelectKBest(k=25)
    selected_features = selector.fit(x,y)
    indices_selected = selected_features.get_support(indices=True)
    columns_selected = [x.columns[i] for i in indices_selected]
    return x[columns_selected]

def select_features_FromModel(x,y,model=None,features_importance=False):
    """
        Select features from coefficients of an estimator
    """
    sel = SelectFromModel(model)
    sel.fit(x,y)
    if features_importance:
        selected_features = x.columns[sel.get_support()]
        df = pd.DataFrame({'Feature':list(selected_features),
                           'Importance':list(sel.estimator_.feature_importances_[sel.get_support()])})
        df = df.sort_values(by='Importance',ascending=False)
        sns.barplot('Feature','Importance',data=df)
        plt.xticks(rotation=90)
        plt.show()
        sel.transform(x),df
        
    return sel.transform(x)

Data visualization: Comparison between predictions and groundtruths¶

In [404]:
def plot_regression_results(ax, y_true, y_pred, title, scores):
    """Scatter plot of the predicted vs true targets."""
    ax.plot([y_true.min(), y_true.max()],
    [y_true.min(), y_true.max()],
    '--r', linewidth=2)
    ax.scatter(y_true, y_pred, alpha=0.2)

    ax.spines['top'].set_visible(False)
    ax.spines['right'].set_visible(False)
    ax.get_xaxis().tick_bottom()
    ax.get_yaxis().tick_left()
    ax.spines['left'].set_position(('outward', 10))
    ax.spines['bottom'].set_position(('outward', 10))
    ax.set_xlim([y_true.min(), y_true.max()])
    ax.set_ylim([y_true.min(), y_true.max()])
    ax.set_xlabel('Measured')
    ax.set_ylabel('Predicted')
    extra = plt.Rectangle((0, 0), 0, 0, fc="w", fill=False,
      edgecolor='none', linewidth=0)
    ax.legend([extra], [scores], loc='upper left')
    title = title
    ax.set_title(title)

Model building¶

In [456]:
def run_model(x,y,estimator):
    """
        Define a tree or gradient based model
    """
    #estimator = RandomForestRegressor(n_estimators=100,n_jobs=-1)
    #model = make_pipeline(RobustScaler(),estimator)
    model = estimator

    cv = KFold(5,shuffle=True)
    score = cross_validate(model,x,y,cv=cv,scoring=['r2', 'neg_mean_squared_error'])
    y_pred = cross_val_predict(model, x, y, cv=cv, n_jobs=-1, verbose=0)
    
    ax = plt.gca()
    plot_regression_results(ax,y,y_pred,'PROTEIN prediction',(r'$R^2={:.2f} \pm {:.2f}$' + '\n' + r'$RMSE={:.6f} \pm {:.6f}$')
                .format(np.mean(score['test_r2']),
                np.std(score['test_r2']),
                np.sqrt(-np.mean(score['test_neg_mean_squared_error'])),
                np.sqrt(np.std(score['test_neg_mean_squared_error']))))
